This is the Repo of the timesheet application of ffa

Version 0.2.1. 
- Version: Upgrade Angular version from 4 to 7
- Scheduler: Bugfixes and replacement of fullcalender component
- Environments: Modify loading of env files for both frontend / backend
- Vacation hrs are now scalled for people starting within the year accordingly (e.g. only ~90% of vacation hrs available when starting in feb of the year )


Version 0.1.1. 
- Account: Display actual time including aux-hours
- Scheduler: Add display details/overview 
- Add no-caching for GET requests to ensure actuality of displayed information
- Timegroupplanner gets all users available for planning in scheduler view
- auto logout after certain period of time 

